                             GLOBE U.S. Partners

   The U.S. GLOBE Program enters into partnerships with U.S. organizations
   which undertake efforts to recruit GLOBE schools, train GLOBE teachers,
   and mentor GLOBE students in their areas. Regions where GLOBE partners
   are active are noted on the map below. Click on a specific state for
   more information about U.S. Partners in that state or use the list icon
   below. If you are interested in more information about the GLOBE U.S.
   Partner concept, please contact info@globe.gov

   See GLOBE U.S. Partners' reports from the 2001 GLOBE Annual Conference

                               [ISMAP:US.gif]

               Click on a state to see a list of U.S. Partners

